Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in cases leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' before moving to any 'Accepted + In Progress' activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time it takes to move from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in cases with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before it
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in cases that eventually reach 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to the next activity, excluding 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Resolved' in the most frequent variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in cases that do not include 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor does not occur

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in cases that include 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before it
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation occurs

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in cases with 'Completed + In Call' as the final activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
